    {
      "lineNumber": 1,
      "text": "September 27, 1947",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 2,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 3,
      "text": "Major General George C. McDonald",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 4,
      "text": "Assistant Chief Air Staff - 2",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 5,
      "text": "The Pentagon",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 6,
      "text": "Washington, D. C.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 7,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "text": "RECORDED",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "62-83894-121",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Dear General McDonald:",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "The Federal Bureau of Investigation has been requested",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "by your office to assist in the investigation of reported sight-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "ings of flying discs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "My attention has been called to instructions disseminated",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "by the Air Forces relative to this matter. I have been advised",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "that these instructions indicate that the Air Forces would inter-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "view responsible observers while the FBI would investigate incidents",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "of discs found on the ground, thereby relieving the Air Forces of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "running down incidents which in many cases turned out to be \"ash",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "can covers, toilet seats and whatnot.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "In view of the apparent understanding by the Air Forces",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "of the position of the Federal Bureau of Investigation in this",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "matter, I cannot permit the personnel and time of this organiza-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "tion to be dissipated in this manner.",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "I am advising the Field Divisions of the Federal Bureau",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "of Investigation to discontinue all investigative activity regard-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "ing the reported sightings of flying discs, and am instructing them",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "to refer all complaints received to the appropriate Air Force",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "representative in their area.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "Sincerely yours,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "J. Edgar Hoover",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
